Hi Drew,

> I have some minor problems still to iron out.  My
> turn signals stopped working, but the hazard
> flashers still work...I'm sure that they share
> the same relay, all I get from the turn signal
> lever is a steady indicator light
> in the dash (left and right) and nothing from the
> lights themselves.

I had the same thing last winter on my 1971 panelvan.
When I slammed the cabin door the turn signal would
blink a few times and then hold still again. I
replaced the relay and since then it works perfectly
again. So I would try replacing the relay if I was
you.



